#### PR description:

- Fix relval crash in JMENano workflows reported in https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/39796#issuecomment-1308612443
- Further remove unused variables and modules from NanoAOD, follow-up of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/39796

#### PR validation:

Nano workflows on the IB I was developing on are temporarily broken because of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/39927#issuecomment-1308338865, hence the WIP status. I will wait for the latest IB and remove the WIP status once things are validated.
title: WIP: Fix JMENano, further cleanup in Nano
